    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) features the 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant with VarioCam Plus, delivering 320 hp through a precise Getrag G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical profile is bolstered by a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced Air-Oil Separator (AOS). The chassis maintains excellent kinematics with its multi-link rear suspension and four-piston monobloc calipers providing consistent thermal management and bite. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain exhibits strong compression and stable oil pressure across the rev range. A driver-focused example with the mechanical sorted for immediate spirited use.",
